high_descs: Turn left and approach the dresser ahead.
Pick up the banana that is on the right end of the dresser.
Exit this room through the doorway on the right and go straight to the side table against the wall to the left.
Place the banana down on the side table.
Return to the room you started in and go towards the left end of the dresser.
Pick up the banana from the dresser.
Return to the side table you placed the first banana on.
Place the second banana down on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place two bananas on a side table.

high_descs: Go straight towards the wall and then walk straight into the room, turning to the dresser on your right.
Pick up banana from the dresser.
Turn right and go straight and make a right turn near side table.
Place banana on the side table.
Turn around and walk to the dresser to your left.
Pick up banana from the dresser.
Turn right and go straight and make a right turn near side table.
Place banana on the side table.
anns.task_desc: Collecting banana from different places and arranging them on a side table.

high_descs: There is a dressed on your left, stand in front of its right side.
Pick up a banana atop the dresser.
Turn right, pass through the entrance in the upper left, continue straight in between a couch on the right and a sidetable on the left, and face the sidetable.
Put the banana on the sidetable.
Go back to the dresser but this time position yourself in front of its left side.
Pick up a banana from the top of the dresser.
Get back to the sidetable.
Put the banana on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Place two bananas on the sidetable.
